verbose_text: We found that IL-8 production in PMNs from diabetic subjects was induced by rIL-1beta in a dose dependent manner, although at lower levels than observed with PMNs from healthy donors (XREF_FIG; P < 0.001 and XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY online).
evidence: IL-8 production in PMNs from diabetic subjects was induced by rIL-1beta
